    "created_at": "2016-08-31T09:22:07Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-31T09:23:31Z",
    "body": "The nice thing about this is that existing applications wouldn't be broken in any way, as placing all the files except for `electron.exe` into a subdirectory would be optional.\n"
